headline: Atlanticus price target raised to $75 from $54 at JMP Securities
summary: JMP Securities analyst David Scharf raised the firm’s price target on Atlanticus (ATLC) to $75 from $54 and keeps an Outperform rating on the shares following the recent expansion of its partnership with Synchrony (SYF).
